      "text": [
        "2272 - وَمَنْ دُفِنَ فِي الْحَرَمِ أَمِنَ مِنَ الْفَزَعِ الْأَكْبَرِ، مِنْ بَرِّ النَّاسِ وَفَاجِرِهِمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2272 - Whoever is buried in the Sacred Sanctuary will be safe from the Great Terror, whether they were righteous or sinful."
